14    /**
15    * This class implements some functions as static class methods.
16    *
17    * It provides functions like
18    * <ul>
19    * <li>the Black-Scholes formula,
20    * <li>the inverse of the Back-Scholes formula with respect to (implied) volatility,
21    * <li>the Bachelier formula,
22    * <li>the inverse of the Bachelier formula with respect to (implied) volatility,
23    * <li>the corresponding functions (versions) for caplets and swaptions,
24    * <li>analytic approximation for European options under the SABR model,
25    * <li>some convexity adjustments.
26    * </ul>
27    *
28    * @author Christian Fries
